## Implementation of the Board of Directors' Duties

Throughout  2023,  the  Board  of  Directors  made  various decisions  aimed  at  supporting  operations  and  achieving the Bank's targets as described below:

- 1. Implementation of the Bank's management;
- 2. Management of the Bank's asset and finances;
- 3. Preparation of the Bank's planning;
- 4. Implementation  of  the  Board  of  Directors  meetings, attending Board of Commissioners meetings and GMS;
- 5. Supervision  and  improvement  of  internal  business processes;
- 6. Determination  of  risk  management  and  governance pillars;
- 7. Fulfillment of the Bank's target performance; and
- 8. Implementation  of  other  duties  related  to  the  Bank management.

