The orientation program for new members of the Board of  Directors  aims  to  enable  the  members  of  the  Board of  Directors  to  get  to  know  and  understand  the  Bank better.  Through  the  orientation  program,  new  members of  the  Board  of  Directors  are  provided  with  information on the Vision, Mission, history, corporate structure, Bank culture  the,  and  other  important  information  about  the Bank, which is coordinated by the Corporate Secretary. In 2023, the Bank held an orientation program for Mr. Edwin Rudianto as a newly appointed member of the Board of Directors in early 2023.

